#10023
The Western Concourse~
The concourse connects the northern and southern sections of the stands.  You
can hear the sounds of vendors selling beer and street food in this area.  
Though there is not any seating, there is limited standing room with a decent
view of the arena.  This is also one of the few shaded areas within the
stands, and can offer a bit of respite from inclement weather or the
suffocating summer heat.  The concourse continues to the south, and exits into
the stands to the north.  
~
