#10028
Entrance to the Podium~
This section of the concourse is much cleaner than the rest of the stands.  
Spectators are quickly ushered through this area of the concourse and
loitering here is not permitted.  There is a wide set of stairs up from here
into the senatorial balconies.  The concourse continues to the north and exits
into the stands to the south.  
