#10032
The Vomitoria~
This large, open chamber leads directly into the stands.  It gradually opens
outward to the east and the west making the many rows of step-like seating
easily accessible.  There are spectators everywhere, jostling you around as
people are constantly entering and leaving the arena.  The stone ground is wet
with spilled beer and water, making it almost treacherously slippery.  There
are two wide staircases leading down into the lobby.  To the south its
possible to move further up onto the stands.  Even from here you already have
a good view of the combat already taking place in the arena below.  
~
