#10041
The Entrance to the Arena~
You are standing in the wide lobby of the arena.  The marble stone beneath
your feet is well worn and littered with pamphlets, tickets, and other various
garbage carelessly tossed out by the throngs of people in the stadium.  
Directly ahead of you is a massive portcullis that leads into the arenas
fighting grounds.  Theres a small vestibule leading to the portcullis wherein
you catch a peek of contenders preparing for battle.  Two broad staircases
lead up into the stands, where the deafening sounds of the crowd above make it
clear there is an exciting spectacle on display.  A smaller staircase in the
vestibule before the portcullis leads down into the arena's staging area.  
~
100 32772 0 0 0 0
D0
Through the iron bars, you see the arena's fighting grounds.
~
portcullis~
