E
pamphlets~
"See the fury of TARG THE TROLL as he crushes his opponents! Don't miss this opportunity - excitement only found in the famous Kir Drax'in Coliseum!"
~
S
#10042
The Grand Archway of the Coliseum~
You are beneath a massive archway that marks the entrance to Kir Drax'in's
coliseum.  You can hear the distinct sounds of men and beasts in combat
punctuated by a raucous cheering from the huge crowd in the stands.  There is
an odd combination of odors here, as you can faintly pick up the sickly-sweet
smells of blood, sweat, and beer.  Large marble pillars line the thoroughfare
to the north leading further into the stadium.  The road south leads back to
the Avenue of the Gods.  
~
100 32768 0 0 0 0
D0
~
~
0 0 10041
D2
~
~
0 0 8071
E
archway~
An imposing marble arch towers above you.  Carved along the top of the archway
are the words, "Omnium Rerum Principia Parva Sunt"
~
E
pillars~
Beautifully designed pillars line the entrance of the coliseum.  Each features
intricate carvings of warriors and beasts.  
~
S
#10043
The Arena~
You are standing on the grounds of the Kir Draxin combat arena.  The sandy
ground is saturated with blood and sweat, but each footfall still manages to
expel a puff of dust.  There are chunks of flesh and pieces of broken
equipment from previous fights sparsely scattered on the ground around you,
despite the best efforts of the staff to clean up between rounds.  The massive
arena engulfs you with expansive grounds and towering spectator stands
everywhere you look.  The cheers of the fans echo around the arena from all
directions.  The arena grounds continue to the north and east.  To the south
there is a massive portcullis blocking the exit of the stadium
~
