#10050
Before the Podium~
This is where the elite of Kir Drax'in come to watch the arena battles.  The
transition from the rest of the stands is startling.  The floors are clean and
well maintained, and the seal of Kir Drax'in's nobility has been carved into
the eastern wall.  There is a staircase leading down back to the concourse
proper.  To the north a pair of large, heavy curtains blocks entry into the
balconies.  
~
