barrels~
The barrels are filled with a pale yellow beer the spectators lovingly refer
to as pisswater.  The large barrels are sitting on the stall counters and are
tapped at the bottom.  They do not, however, have lids, and you can see dead
insects and other debris floating on the beer's surface.  None of this seems
to bother anyone else, though.  
~
