#10057
Entrance to the Staging Area~
This dark and dimly lit hallway leads into the arena's staging area.  There is
a pronounced odor of death, blood, and sweat down here.  Underground, there's
simply no place for the rotten air to escape other than through this hallway
into the arena entrance above.  There's a lot of activity here, with people
moving bodies and equipment in and out of the arena.  A couple of contenders
are discussing tactics for their upcoming fight, as they prepare to move into
the lobby above.  Massive stone blocks line the walls of the hallway.  There
is a stairwell heading up into the lobby, and the corridor continues north
further into the staging area.  
~
