#10058
A Dimly Lit Hallway Beneath the Arena~
Deeper into the staging area, the scent of death and blood becomes
overpowering, though no one around seems to notice.  Lit only by torches and a
small grate above struggling to vent the noxious fumes, it is a sharp contrast
from the arena's exterior.  The corridor continues onward to the north.  To
the east is a preparation room for combatants, and to the west are the beast
pens.  Whether it is poor design, or the managers of the arena just like
frightening the upcoming combatants, the beasts are clearly visible from the
preparation rooms.  There is a reinforced barred door keeping the beasts in
the pen.  
~
