#10060
The Beast Pens~
These pen are where the keep the beasts for upcoming battles.  Torn up raw
meat lies rotting on the floor.  Whether fed to the beasts by uncaring
keepers, or the result of fights between the bests themselves, it saturates
the air with a festering stink.  The air here is almost cloudy with flies and
gnats feasting upon the rotting meat, and the floor is slick with blood.  
However it is the keepers manage to move animals in and out of here with any
order is a mystery.  There is a large reinforced barred door to the east
keeping the beasts in their pens.  
~
