#10061
A Dimly Lit Hallway Beneath the Arena~
At the back end of the staging area, the grotesque nature of the arena becomes
evident.  Blood trails lead to both the east and the west.  To the east is the
triage room where injured combatants are taken for medical assistance.  To the
west is the "disposal" room where corpses, both beast and man, are taken to be
eliminated.  Surrounded by injury, death, and rot, you find it quite difficult
to breath.  To the south the hallway continues toward the exit of the staging
area.  
~
