#10062
The Arena's Triage Chamber~
Hanging on the walls of this room are a myriad of crude medical devices still
coated with the brown remnants of coagulated blood.  There is a single table
in the middle of the room, also stained with old blood.  Presumably this is
where injured combatants are lain for operation.  Cabinets filled with
bandages and other miscellaneous surgical items line the eastern wall.  To the
west is the main hallway of the staging area.  
~
