#10063
The Arena's Disposal Chambers~
This is where the corpses from combat are taken to be disposed.  There's a
large furnace with a gated opening on the western wall.  In the middle of the
room there is what appears to be a well, although the smell emanating from the
pit would suggest otherwise.  Along the walls hang saws and hammers of various
sizes, suggesting that some corpses are...  Reduced...  Prior to being "taken
care of". A crude hand-written sign hangs on the northern wall.  The eastern
door heads into the staging area corridor.  
~
