#10064
The Bottom of the Arena's Disposal Well~
You immediately realize that being here is a huge mistake.  The only natural
light in this room is the pale speck of the well's opening, which is far, far
out of reach.  The cobbled brick that was lining the wall gave way to burrowed
dirt and stone.  The liquid at the bottom of this well is blood, not water.  
Perhaps curiosity shouldn't have gotten the best of you.  
~
